  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Realising the potential of responsible ASGM trade</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Goal of this project: preservation of 10 gold ASMs in the Geita region, Tanzania.Solidaridad and The Impact Facility are already collaborating with these mines.Certification is difficult or impossible (expensive) for these types of mines and The Impact Facility has set up an alternative ESG structure with basic, intermediate and advanced levels, where advanced equals the level of certification. These mines vary between basic and intermediate. The most pressing problems are:&#x2022;	the use of mercury (disastrous for people and the environment), which is the most efficient and cheap method of gold mining, and&#x2022;	at random digging, instead of using geodata (expensive).</narrative>
  </description>
